Description: Ash Blake attends the Ansarivan Dragonar Academy, where each student rides their own dragon. But Ash's dragon, Eco, is different and can transform into a human girl.
Title: DRAGONAR ACADEMY, VOL. 2
Author: Shiki Mizuchi and Ran

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 3
Author: Okayado

Description: Crona goes on a killing spree in Moscow at the behest of Medusa. Will Maka be able to stop him?
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 20
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Issei Hyodo’s first date with Yuma Amano does end well. Instead of a goodnight kiss, she kills him! But his death is only the beginning, when he is reincarnated as a devil.
Title: HIGH SCHOOL DXD, VOL. 1
Author: Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima
Contributor: by Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima

Description: Erwin and the Survey Corps launch a dangerous mission to rescue Eren from the Colossus and Armored Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 12
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The 104th Training Corps stop for a much–needed respite in Utgard Castle, but their plans to rest are foiled when they discover that the Titans are now attacking at night.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 10
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, the Titans attack, but one of them goes rogue.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 2
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Hana meets and falls in love with a man who is a werewolf, but when tragedy strikes, she is forced to raise their children alone in this adaptation of the animated film.
Title: WOLF CHILDREN: AME AND YUKI
Author: Mamoru Hosoda and Yu

Description: Erza, Gajeel and Laxus reach the finals of The Grand Magic Games but those events pale in comparison to another shocking development: the return of the dragons.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 38
Author: Hiro Mashima
